tainers with everyday maintenance tasks. It consists of utilities to&nbsp;assist with &nbsp;database functions, database backup, FTP transfers, log file clearance, upgrade preparation, site search and link checking.</p>\n<p>It utilises robust 3rd party applications such as SQLBuddy and integrates them into a single component giving site administrators a single tool to use &nbsp;from one place, rather than a plethora of external ones as is usually the case.</p>\n<p>Please read the User Guide in /assets/components/janitor/docs before using this component, especially the section on Security.</p>\n<p>This version is functionally complete except for the Events tab, this is still under development.</p>\n<p>The FTP client has been changed from phpMyWebFTP to eXtplorer, this gives a combined FTP client and file browser capable of archiving content.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\";s:8:\"children\";a:0:{}}i:13;a:4:{s:4:\"name\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:0:{}s:4:\"text\";s:60:\"<p>Install as normal through Revolutions package manager</p>\";s:8:\"children\";a:0:{}}i:14;a:4:{s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:0:{}s:4:\"text\";s:76:\"<p>Updates for Revolution 2.2, github ticket fixes, maintenance release.</p>\";s:8:\"children\";a:0:{}}i:15;a:4:{s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"createdon\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:0:{}s:4:\"text\";s:24:\"2012-03-29T10:16:50+0000\";s:8:\"children\";a:0:{}}i:16;a:4:{s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"createdby\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:0:{}s:4:\"text\";s:9:\"shamblett\";s:8:\"children\";a:0:{}}i:17;a:4:{s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"editedon\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:0:{}s:4:\"text\";s:24:\"2017-07-04T09:27:02+0000\";s:8:\"children\";a:0:{}}i:18;a:4:{s:4:\"name\";s:10:\"releasedon\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:0:{}s:4:\"text\";s:24:\"2012-03-29T10:16:50+0000\";s:8:\"children\";a:0:{}}i:19;a:4:{s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"downloads\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:0:{}s:4:\"text\";s:4:\"6316\";s:8:\"children\";a:0:{}}i:20;a:4:{s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"approved\";s:10:\"attributes\";a:0:{}s:4:\"text\";s